Package net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data.event

Events specific to data models live here.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ColumnModelListener
    Events dealing with changes in a ColumnModel.
    ListDataListener
    ListDataListener for events dealing with lists of data.
    ListSelectionListener
    Listener for ListSelectionModel events.
    TableModelListener
    TableModelListener defines the interface for an object that listens to changes in a TableModel.
    TreeModelListener
    The interface for objects that listen to TreeModel events.
    TreeSelectionListener
    The listener that's notified when the selection in a TreeSelectionModel changes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColumnModelEvent
    ColumnModelEvent is used to notify listeners that a table column model has changed, such as a column was added, removed, or moved.
    ListDataEvent  
    ListSelectionEvent
    Event object for ListSelectionListener.
    TableModelEvent
    The event object for TableModel events.
    TreeModelEvent
    The event object for a TreeModel.
    TreeSelectionEvent
    The event object for TreeSelectionListener events.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ColumnModelEventType
    Event types for column model events.
    ListDataEventType
    List data event types.
    TableModelEventType
    Enumeration of TableModelEvent types.
    TreeModelEventType
    Tree model event types.

Package net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data.event Description

Events specific to data models live here. Please refer to the listener and event class documentation for detailed documentation.
